<subsection>

  <title>
    Adjustments Due to Covid-19 (or any illness)
  </title>
    <p>
      If at any point during the semester I am unable to physically
      attend class on campus, but am otherwise able to teach (due to
      Covid, or whatever), we will
      switch to an online teaching mode via Zoom. I will explain how
      this will all work at that time, should it ever
      occur. Hopefully, it never will.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you are unable to attend class due to illness, I will be
      flexible as long as you keep me informed. Contact me as soon as
      you possibly can.
    </p>
</subsection>



